  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>κοιμητήρην Βαλερεία[ς] <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>κ(αὶ) Εὐκαρπεία[ς <span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\">l.1 reg., orig. ην</p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>ΚΟΙΜΗΤΗΡΗΝΒΑΛΕΡΕΙΑ[.]<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ΚΕΥΚΑΡΠΕΙΑ[.<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\">l.1 reg., orig. ην</p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text after Manganaro, with correction of Feissel</span></span>; </li><li><span class=\"1\">1: <span>Manganaro: Βαλερείου</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>Resting place of Baleria and Eukarpeia [---]</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Reported by Manganaro from original publication by Di Stefano.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 54.0879 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> 2006.0566 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282</a></li><li> Di Stefano 1991 32-33 </li><li> Manganaro 2005 42 n.34 fig.3-4 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001799\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001799</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
